       IDENTIFICATION   DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.      prog.
       DATA             DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE  SECTION.
       01 SINGLE-ITEM   PIC X(999999999).
       01 GROUP-ITEM1.
          05 FILLER     PIC X(999999999).
       01 GROUP-ITEM2.
          05 FILLER     PIC X(199999999).
          05 FILLER     PIC X(199999999).
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
           STOP RUN.

])

